  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This package documents the simulation credibility evidence for a CFD-based hemolysis prediction model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. The model has been applied in clinical research settings to support worst-case operating condition identification for Class II cardiopulmonary bypass devices. A full 13-factor ASME V&V 40 assessment was conducted at Model Risk Level 2, with 7 factors formally assessed and 6 scoped out as not required at this risk level. All assessed factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The assessment supports a regulatory submission decision under the Minimal credibility profile.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cpb-worst-case-hemolysis",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v2",
