      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal numerical solver error characterization beyond code verification is not required; Gradation 1 (awareness) is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Solver error is addressed implicitly through code verification and discretization error assessment. Standalone numerical solver error factor not assessed per MRL 2 scoping; Gradation 1 requirement satisfied by awareness documentation."
    },
