      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was selected based on published literature. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged; formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. Gradation 1 met."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
