      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU need only be qualitatively acknowledged at Gradation 1.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative comparison between validation test inputs and intended CPB operating envelope has been documented. Formal equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2. Gradation 1 criterion met."
